memberdef.name: YYSTACK_RELOCATE
memberdef.initializer: do \ { \ YYSIZE_T yynewbytes; \ YYCOPY (&yyptr->Stack_alloc, Stack, yysize); \ Stack = &yyptr->Stack_alloc; \ yynewbytes = yystacksize * sizeof (*Stack) + YYSTACK_GAP_MAXIMUM; \ yyptr += yynewbytes / sizeof (*yyptr); \ } \ while (YYID (0))

memberdef.name: YYCOPY
memberdef.initializer: do \ { \ YYSIZE_T yyi; \ for (yyi = 0; yyi < (Count); yyi++) \ (Dst)[yyi] = (Src)[yyi]; \ } \ while (YYID (0))

memberdef.name: YYBACKUP
memberdef.initializer: do \ if (yychar == YYEMPTY) \ { \ yychar = (Token); \ yylval = (Value); \ YYPOPSTACK (yylen); \ yystate = *yyssp; \ goto yybackup; \ } \ else \ { \ yyerror (yyscanner, jsgf, YY_("syntax error: cannot back up")); \ YYERROR; \ } \ while (YYID (0))
